Package: TjSuper
Title: Tools for Advanced Medical Statistics and Biomedical Research
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(
        given = "Tjssn",
        family = "Development Team",
        email = "tongjibbb@163.com",
        role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
Description: Provides an integrated toolkit for advanced medical statistics,
    clinical research analytics, machine learning, deep learning, automated
    statistical table generation, weighted analysis, standardized mean
    difference analysis, data visualization, example datasets, and standardized
    Word report generation. The package aims to support a wide range of
    biomedical research workflows, including clinical medicine, public health,
    epidemiology, psychology, nursing, laboratory medicine, and real-world
    data analysis.
